Class Level

  • java.lang.Object
    • Level

  • public class Level
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents a level. Contains the data for each level as well. Initializes an engine to actually run the game.
    Version:
    May 18, 2018
    Author:
    Roshan Sevalia, Period: 4, Assignment: APCSfinal, Sources: Gaurav Vipat, Charlie Huang
